CHROMATIC_17_LASER_CAVITY_KERNEL
first_author: David Wise
mode: local_simulation_only

TOPOLOGY
  16 spectrum emitters
  4 emitters per quadrant
  17th point = pure white coherence core

NODES
  L01 red_pressure
  L02 orange_gain
  L03 amber_transition
  L04 yellow_lift
  L05 lime_correction
  L06 green_stability
  L07 mint_expansion
  L08 cyan_edge
  L09 azure_carrier
  L10 blue_coherence
  L11 indigo_depth
  L12 violet_gate
  L13 magenta_return
  L14 rose_inversion
  L15 crimson_lock
  L16 infra_red_floor
  C17 pure_white_core

RULE
  contain_target = 0.98
  output_coupling = 0.02
  quadrant_count = 4
  beams_per_quad = 4

LOOP
  SAMPLE phase[16]
  NORMALIZE amplitude[16]
  BALANCE each quadrant
  SUM into C17
  CLAMP color dominance
  RELEASE controlled white output
  FOLD drift back into containment curve
  REPORT coherence
  REPEAT

BOUNDARY
  simulation is conceptual and visual
  no physical laser construction parameters
